  "body": "<h1>FullGrownCropMarker</h1>\n<h4>Adds a little marker over all crops that are at their maximum age!</h4>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/gD7GDSB/Full-Grown-Crop-Marker.png\" alt=\"FullGrownCropMarker\"></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nThis mod is a client-side only mod, it is not required to be installed on the server.\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nif you have any questions about the mod, or you want a few insights about upcoming features:\n<br>\nfeel free to join the Discord &nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VQ66pHN/Discord.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"166\" height=\"32\" />\n</a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">link</a>\n",
